The room was exceptionally spacious, the bathroom well stocked with towels, robes and toiletries.	The bathroom was big, with plenty of fluffy towels and the bedroom had a large TV with a good selection of channels.	The tub/shower door was so short that the minute you turned on the shower, water gets all over the bathroom.	One small negative was the sink, which was located in the room rather than the bathroom.	Our 5th floor room was spacious, contemporary and very comfortable (pictures posted) and the bathroom was good sized.	The room and large bathroom were clean and orderly.